
{center}
{subhead} PD Toplist{def}{p}
{left}
{p} {p}

This is a new section in AIO, we are testing to see if the readers are
willing to send an email each month and vote on their favourite util.
{p} {p}
So, please send Your votes to us and hopefully we will gather a nice list.
It's not that hard to send one mail a month! And it can help people notice
software that they didn't know of... Who knows, You might find a new
software that You can't understand how You have been able to live without!
{p} {p}
To send Your votes, send a mail to {bold}lorens@aio.co.uk{nobold} with the subject:{p}
{bold}AIO Toplist{nobold}
{p} {p}
You must choose three programs, You will give 3 points to the one You like
the most, 2 points to the second, and 1 point to the third!
{p} {p}
{image 25_PDTopList.IFF}
{p} {p}
{p} {p}
So, {bold}PLEASE{nobold} take 2 minutes and vote for this! Show your support!
